  <brief_title>CYT003-QbG10 for Treatment of Allergic Asthma Bronchial</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Assess Pharmacodynamic and Clinical Efficacy of CYT003-QbG10 in Patients With Persistent Allergic Asthma Bronchial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
