  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to test whether treatment with CYT003-QbG10 can improve asthma
      symptoms in patients with allergic bronchial asthma. The active treatment will be compared
      against placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
